{
  "title": "Magical Silky Egyptian Chicken Curry",
  "description": "A spicy and silky Egyptian dish featuring panang paste, steam, and ayurvedic rajasic friendly ingredients, this curry is a quick fix for any meal. It combines the flavors of Egypt with the warmth of Indian spices.",
  "cuisine": "Egyptian",
  "diet": [
